# $Header: /var/cvsroot/gentoo-x86/media-tv/mythtv/ChangeLog,v 1.426 2015/03/22 07:44:29 nativemad Exp $

  22 Mar 2015; Andreas Schuerch <nativemad@gentoo.org>
  mythtv-0.27_p20140321.ebuild:
  x86 stable, see bug 508200

*mythtv-0.27.4_p20150124 (24 Jan 2015)

  24 Jan 2015; Richard Freeman <rich0@gentoo.org>
  +mythtv-0.27.4_p20150124.ebuild:
  Patch update.

  12 Dec 2014; Sergey Popov <pinkbyte@gentoo.org> metadata.xml:
  USE='vaapi' is now global, removing it's description from metadata

*mythtv-0.27.4_p20141018 (20 Oct 2014)

  20 Oct 2014; Richard Freeman <rich0@gentoo.org>
  +mythtv-0.27.4_p20141018.ebuild:
  Bump, new patches.

*mythtv-0.27.3_p20141009 (11 Oct 2014)

  11 Oct 2014; Richard Freeman <rich0@gentoo.org>
  +mythtv-0.27.3_p20141009.ebuild:
  Update 0.27 fixes.

*mythtv-0.27.3_p20140907 (08 Sep 2014)

  08 Sep 2014; Richard Freeman <rich0@gentoo.org>
